{"tid":1633890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月1日係最能夠展現咩叫核爆都唔割","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:40:29.000Z","uid":38212,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"17cee545993421c65609bef885e41acf7d760958","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"記得當日我喺電視見到阻止升旗禮失敗之後<br />\n<br />\n大家休息咗成個上晝<br />\n<br />\n連防暴都走埋唔理你班人<br />\n<br />\n之後下午時分開始衝立會<br />\n<br />\n好多人第一時間嘅反應係：做乜鳩？又話之後join遊行？<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋最後係返返嚟立會呢邊 傳物資又好湊人數做FA都好<br />\n<br />\n之後遊行班和理非到咗金鐘之後好多係轉咗右邊嚟夏愨道<br />\n<br />\n甚至連民陣都暗示話你可以去立會嗰邊唔一定要跟佢哋行<br />\n<br />\n到衝擊完之後大家雖然有屌下又有外國媒體話我哋暴力<br />\n<br />\n但大家係出盡奶力做文宣 <br />\n<br />\n又打上電台解釋 <br />\n<br />\n又會放大我哋做嘅好事（抬人走，飲嘢畀錢嗰啲）<br />\n<br />\n嗰時甚至係淺黃嘅都俾我哋打動到<br />\n<br />\n但點解到咗而家又係打爛玻璃又係破壞<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然口講唔割但實際上屌得最金嘅又係自己友？<br />\n<br />\n我最心痛唔係啲藍絲屌多兩錢重或者啲所謂淺黃想割<br />\n<br />\n而係連我哋自己友都唔團結開始內鬨<br />\n<br />\n有做得唔好嘅 過則勿憚改<br />\n<br />\n但如果我哋自己都唔團結一致<br />\n<br />\n又何談去說服其他人？<br />\n<br />\n所以我喺度跪求大家今日唔好再不停內鬨<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割唔係口號<br />\n<br />\n係要做出嚟㗎<br />\n<br />\n就趁今日文宣日大家先暫停內鬨<br />\n<br />\n槍口一致對外先好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8c0069b23a84016c5e2e23f2cbee2acaea9bf7","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2faebb33db713003247fd2f25a8d1175b20032b7","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"2ee41f094ca04b43d40bd39726f6b1076b73c949","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7907ca89d73ea8cf0e8c05ea16f07b318a8a074e","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9733472d109b2c27a0b302f1eed80a322a0c69cd","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"df99c2803970916a721ed9422677996198a97427","tid":1633890,"uid":79957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"推，唔好再玩標籤<br />\n要記住世上只有我們是香港人"},{"pid":"ea1f36ad7796c3449e6c5b6794ea7476088ad367","tid":1633890,"uid":14478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"因為未撚訓醒 人地槍都開埋有班撚屌屌鳩人裝修 要停一停<br />\n<br />\n我同你地講 一停個熱實輸 一輸 一定係大規模搜捕"},{"pid":"019d6eb78803658aeacbd99ab88a11e818f34d7a","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"084ccf2857d4cf7fbf60c18f69019fed7c95f592","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91926d3782f714f1465bd776858f7d0cd40a908e","tid":1633890,"uid":167421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c1cd454face1f3e01c7ebf378b9949e5ca9bd77","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"a27f71d5d6399954992b434d271751c5275e15e4","tid":1633890,"uid":217004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c62f4eb0df00238d6e4ecd3f4729032a8c302f","tid":1633890,"uid":40748,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"最簡單回歸初心 就係 兄弟爬山 各自努力 不分化不割蓆<br />\n面對政府陰謀 更加係要團結 而家黑警落重兵力搞緊晒連登 但你上其他地方 根本個撚個都屌黑警政府 係得呢到自亂陣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a928116ccbc7991f05eb69382a78eefc9fae5b4a","tid":1633890,"uid":331650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"投降吧黑警，仲有條生路俾你同家人<br />\n10/10 deadline<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ejwexT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ejwexT</a><br />\n<br />\n解散警隊，刻不容緩。<br />\n指證黑警，放你一馬。"},{"pid":"152559e65b154e246aa3831623103871ea2a6e38","tid":1633890,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"呢d先有用post 推"},{"pid":"c8d7322028d34293b75ddeb38d79ed8d6245f8ad","tid":1633890,"uid":76960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"唔會割但要檢討<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c57f98496b7596cf6ec2bf6c9d4b487fdafeaa5","tid":1633890,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c1cd454face1f3e01c7ebf378b9949e5ca9bd77","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"4個月黎連登多左7萬幾個USER<br />\n自己諗有幾多個真係香港人黎"},{"pid":"a3d5bbbf754c1a5fc3ebe25467a862daee0ac40c","tid":1633890,"uid":89873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全港最黃嘅光時網物平台於10月7日上線啦!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629141</a>"},{"pid":"f34e71cb55245e8ce09a36fe21d1e3230e9f883f","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d26b2b2acba12b37b2cf1bafe0292575e28d0dc2","tid":1633890,"uid":121387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"根本就好多三毛<br />\n睇睇fb有撚人割咩"},{"pid":"9c46786b0a90baf2852ed25a15bc1f9ad8c72b88","tid":1633890,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"