88","tid":1633890,"uid":48409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJXO5cr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJXO5cr.jpg&h=ecd3ac7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a86757a67b925977f99a2066cf1e993b6b1bf59b","tid":1633890,"uid":238746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ee77984a5a121aaffbd2f0941f00f1aebff25e2","tid":1633890,"uid":289134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定！"},{"pid":"0f6a900cf1ada490b9baf95816d2074e5214bfad","tid":1633890,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"唔割"},{"pid":"90a18e91013664fb081ab69b085b4d6f90d97488","tid":1633890,"uid":134206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89a0f9772d0314e852b49522bb0d8b986856f182","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da6f218a6a56eb790156b60ecc00026f37fb6c1","tid":1633890,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"我唔會去捉邊個係鬼亦唔會將屌前線嘅人全部當係鬼<br />\n<br />\n但的確係有鬼有三毛喺度煽風點火務求動搖我哋嘅信念<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個時候我哋嘅信念嘅意志先要更加堅定<br />\n<br />\n無論心態上定行動上<br />\n<br />\n所以我先喺度多口講幾句希望團結大家"},{"pid":"a4b3e64a0e157c51dcda5e403fb10ea9ac117d9f","tid":1633890,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"81f9b30891da37820dd1908937f0ed1d4fc873fa","tid":1633890,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"請支持民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n&bull;&nbsp;25m<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家要搞清楚三點啦<br />\n<br />\n1・由始至終&nbsp;由星期五晚起 都係講星期六休息做好文宣 星期日和理非場 星期一18區行動以實行星期二大三罷效果<br />\n2・連登冇熄過燈 一直可以討論行動 點解之前冇人提出過星期一休息e個論點？<br />\n3・有決定後 行動當日無端端有人吹風做其他 仲反咬返堅持原定計畫既人係鬼、冇腦、唔識野<br />\n<br />\n我想問大家 邊個係鬼？堅持星期一實行18區既係鬼 定吹風休息果班係鬼？"},{"pid":"8a5d7414b962fc0d36b2fe27d52403e0f092df63","tid":1633890,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"因為，我地比人分化得好緊要。共產黨既宣傳機器已經火力全開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（公投）如何懲罰HK01? 死紅媒係咁帶風向分化我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"032cc82b9954fa9d171a4d68604730dc5a72a9c9","tid":1633890,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c1cd454face1f3e01c7ebf378b9949e5ca9bd77","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"好多鬼扮自己人<br />\n批評可以，但互屌真係唔好"},{"pid":"22319b4da34c6b9d3344d452b41f01ee5076237a","tid":1633890,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"文宣方向<br />\n放大示威者人性光輝 文明果d野：eg 爆完無拎過貨品 <br />\n強調目的 針對原因"},{"pid":"e01139a04991f0341856aed6c62032e73ab850a9","tid":1633890,"uid":10819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"c5e668a1e1af547ec5a272f4657017aa37dc970a","tid":1633890,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"b36954e64209faeff26a6df3c881705a87510cef","tid":1633890,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘初衷，保持憤怒</span></span>"},{"pid":"5589638ea32560184a2fa3233c7670798f6ba09f","tid":1633890,"uid":242623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"文宣啊"},{"pid":"0c3cb860472808662b7ae531e9b26c26d9c9c35c","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22319b4da34c6b9d3344d452b41f01ee5076237a","tid":1633890,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"文宣方向<br />\n放大示威者人性光輝 文明果d野：eg 爆完無拎過貨品 <br />\n強調目的 針對原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n<br />\n71嗰日成個fb都係立場姐姐喊條片 仲有不破壞文物圖書館 飲嘢要畀錢嘅相 跟住comment 個個都話喊晒口<br />\n<br />\n既然我哋而家係出師有名 只係目標唔同咗 點解就會做唔好到我哋嘅形象？<br />\n<br />\n之前都有人講過話勇武裝修完和理非就喺門口貼文宣 同噴大字寫明唔會偷嘢<br />\n<br />\n亦都有條片講過啲示威者走返嚟捉喺裝修咗嘅舖到偷嘢嘅人<br />\n<br />\n又有啲示威者幫手指揮交通 同裝修完遞紙巾嘅片<br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁好嘅材料點解唔煲大佢？"},{"pid":"f022a91a21db5b94933c5fe135c2a84b0f2b8a7c","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed076a362bc4036e157f2879977d44500d989601","tid":1633890,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"因為支那01上黎帶風向。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280b0a4180260246238e48fba8a95ebfa51f8ece","tid":1633890,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-0